univention-grub (5.0.9-3) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add a new UCR variable grub/generate-menu-lst (set by default), which
    generates a /boot/grub/menu.lst in the Grub 1 format. This is needed to
    boot virtualised Xen UCS instances on Xen installation with an old
    PyGrub. Existing /boot/grub/menu.lst files, which do not contain the
    string "auto-generated through univention-grub-generate-menu-lst" are
    not modified (usually present from updated systems using chainloading).
    Bug #25981

 -- Moritz Muehlenhoff <muehlenhoff@univention.de>  Tue, 14 Feb 2012 15:24:05 +0100

